description:
Deception is a choice. 

God knows that our spirit is in Danger Of Deception. We are weak to temptation. So, we need to take heed of  Deception In Spiritualism. God discerns that work of great deceiver, and He wants to guard our souls. Let us  Seek For The Truth in His words. Do not be deceived by what you think is right. Always be guided by the truth.

Set yourself free from worldly deception. God loves you. He is calling and inviting you. Hear His voice. Turn away from evil. #DoNotBeDeceived by false doctrines. Endow yourself with God's words. #SeekforGodwisdom and #prayforGodsleading. 

Watch the series of Seventh-day Adventist #VirtualGlobalCampmeeting with #Sermon2 entitled, "Deceiving Spirit." Listen to God's instrument, Yvonne Shelton, a woman of God who gave up her career and chose to set herself free from deception. Be inspired by her story and message. Pray for His leading and willingly say, I Will Go.

To follow our official social media accounts, just follow the links below:

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/adventistchurch/
